metadata.name: shore to deep waters
metadata.description: this photo was taken at about 6:30 am on coney island beach a day that i stayed up all night taking photos and trying to push through the night to live another day. this photo was taken when i was at my very lowest. i thought i'd never see the light of day and i did. i saw the next day. i saw a beautiful sunrise. and i took photos all day. but i thought this would be the last photo i ever took. im glad it wasnt.
